item.title: Seminyak 1
item.description: Seminyak Day 1 Today was migration day! We’re finally leaving Ubud and heading to Seminyak. Seminyak is allegedly the more upmarket area of Bali. Kind of like Kuta but more expensive. We had a driver that took us all the way there. Accomodation The AirBnB was located on DoubleSix street, one of the main streets heading into the Double Six Beach. It was actually pretty nice, except for the fact that the internet didn’t work.
